<page section="release-3.10.0">
  <heading>Release 3.10.0</heading>

  <content>
    <para>
      <release-info version="3.10.0" />
      The 3.10.0 release fixes the following issues.
    </para>

    <table class="release-notes">
      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Updated visualizations.
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            FoamTree and Circles visualization updated to their newest versions.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Workbench compatibility fixes (Gnome)
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            Workbench could crash on newer Gnome distributions.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      
      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Lucene and dependency upgrades
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            All library dependencies have been
            upgraded to their newest versions.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      
      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Java 1.7 is now required
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            Java 1.6 reached EOL. Java 1.7 is now required to run
            Carrot2
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="head">
          Bisecting KMeans algorithm bug fixes
        </td>

        <td>
          <p>
            A bug in Bisecting K-Means Clustering could result in 
            incorrect document assignments.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      
    </table>

    <hr />

    <p>
      For a complete list of improvements and bug fixes, see <a href="http://goo.gl/Ime2bf">JIRA</a> 
    </p>
  </content>
</page>

